{% comment %}
  PRNTD — Immersive Homepage
  Rebrand v2 — February 2026
  
  Structure:
  1. Full-screen hero with circular reveal interaction
  2. Editorial product showcase (current drop)
  3. Storytelling divider
  4. Archive teaser
  5. Minimal footer
{% endcomment %}

{% comment %} ============================================================
   SECTION 1: IMMERSIVE HERO
   ============================================================ {% endcomment %}

<section id="prntd-hero">
  {% comment %} 
    Layer Architecture (v2):
    - Layer 1 (base): Always visible, z-index 1
    - Layer 2 (reveal): Hidden in DOM, loaded by JS as Image object, 
      drawn onto reveal canvas only within spotlight regions
    - Reveal Canvas: z-index 2, draws Layer 2 pixels in spotlight areas
    - Grid Canvas: z-index 3, subtle animated grid
    - UI Elements: z-index 10, parallax + inversion
  {% endcomment %}

  {% comment %} Layer 1 — Base image, always visible {% endcomment %}
  {% if settings.hero_layer_1 %}
    <img class="hero-layer-1" src="{{ settings.hero_layer_1 | image_url: width: 2000 }}" alt="PRNTD" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high">
  {% else %}
    <img class="hero-layer-1" src="{{ 'prntd-hero-layer-1.png' | asset_url }}" alt="PRNTD" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high">
  {% endif %}

  {% comment %} Layer 2 — Hidden in DOM, loaded by hero-interaction.js for canvas drawing {% endcomment %}
  {% if settings.hero_layer_2 %}
    <img class="hero-layer-2" src="{{ settings.hero_layer_2 | image_url: width: 2000 }}" alt="" loading="eager" aria-hidden="true">
  {% else %}
    <img class="hero-layer-2" src="{{ 'prntd-hero-layer-2.png' | asset_url }}" alt="" loading="eager" aria-hidden="true">
  {% endif %}

  {% comment %} UI Elements — positioned absolutely, parallax + inversion {% endcomment %}

  {% comment %} Logo — Top Left {% endcomment %}
  <div class="hero-ui hero-logo" data-hero-ui>
    <a href="{{ routes.root_url }}">P.</a>
  </div>

  {% comment %} Nav — Top Right {% endcomment %}
  <div class="hero-ui hero-nav" data-hero-ui>
    <a href="/collections/all">Shop</a>
  </div>

  {% comment %} Social — Bottom Right {% endcomment %}
  <div class="hero-ui hero-social" data-hero-ui>
    <a href="https://instagram.com/prntdbybdq" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Instagram">
